discourse_list.title: First Moonshot Collective (Rapid Prototyping Workstream) call is tomorrow!

content.content: Hey everyone heads up that the first Moonshot Collective Workstream  call is tomorrow at 12pm MST. Sign up at https://moonshotcollective.space/ to get the calendar invite  For more details on the what/why behind this checkout [Workstream] dApp *Prototyping* (the Moonshot Collective)  or check this out below:   We are the GitcoinDAO rapid prototyping workstream. Our deep reason for being is to accelerate innovation by  supporting rapid prototyping in the space   help builders build moonshots   to create fellowship for web3 builders   to HAVE fun while doing it.     Agenda:  G&A (5-10 min) Moonshot Pitches (40 mins) Moonshart Celebrations (10 min) Chat, Chillin’, Shillin   Prep Work:  Please enter your moonshot pitch into https://sli.do (code MOONSHOT) prior to the call. Got any moonSHARTS (failed projects)? Come prepared to share the story of how they failed & what you learned!   Slide Deck: Moonshot Collective Call 0x0 - 7/26/2021 - Google Slides  Zoom Link: Launch Meeting - Zoom
